---
<footer data-orb="3" style="border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
  <div class="page-container" style="padding-top: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 4rem); padding-bottom: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 4rem);">
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr; gap: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); margin-bottom: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 4rem);">
      <div>
        <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">elly</h3>
        <p class="body-small" style="max-width: 280px; font-size: 0.875rem;">Self-hosted AI notebook. Notes, diary, calendar, habits, budget, tasks, AI assistant. Your data, yours.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 style="font-size: 0.6875rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-ink-tertiary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Product</h4>
        <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem;">
          <li><a href="https://www.patreon.com/cw/ellyai?utm_medium=unknown&utm_source=join_link&utm_campaign=creatorshare_creator&utm_content=copyLink" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary); text-decoration: none;">Patreon</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
      <span class="geo-circle" style="background: var(--color-geo-blue);"></span>
      <span class="geo-circle" style="background: var(--color-geo-coral);"></span>
      <span class="geo-circle" style="background: var(--color-geo-teal);"></span>
      <span class="geo-circle" style="background: var(--color-geo-amber);"></span>
    </div>
    <div style="height: 1px; background: var(--color-border); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;"></div>
    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
      <p class="body-small" style="font-size: 0.75rem;">No tracking. Your hardware, your data.</p>
      <p class="body-small" style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-geo-blue);">Built with care.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
